@startuml Delete_Blog_Policy_Sequence_Diagram
title 3.20.5 Delete Blog & Policy - Sequence Diagram
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
autonumber
autoactivate on

actor "Staff/Admin" as User
boundary "Blog & Policy List" as Page
control "ManagePublicContentController" as Controller
control "PublicContentService" as Service
entity "PublicContentDAO" as DAO
database "Database" as DB
boundary "content-list.jsp" as ListView

User -> Page: Delete a blog or policy
Page -> Controller: GET /staff/public-content?action=delete&id={id}
Controller -> Controller: Read content id
Controller -> Service: delete(contentId, currentUser)
Service -> Service: Check permission
Service -> DAO: softDelete(contentId)
DAO -> DB: Mark content as deleted
DB --> DAO: Delete result
DAO --> Service: Delete result
Service --> Controller: Delete successful
Controller -> ListView: Redirect to content list
ListView --> User: Display updated content list

@enduml
